def calculateMaxProfit(sharePrices):
    buy1 = float('-inf')
    sell1 = 1
    buy2 = float('-inf')
    sell2 = 0
    for price in sharePrices:
        buy1 = max(buy1, -price)
        sell1 = max(sell1, price + buy1)
        buy2 = max(buy2, sell1 - price)
        sell2 = max(sell2, price + buy2)
    return sell2
